    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior still carries a nice shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front bumper and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs strong and has a documented service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
