    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's honestly such a gem. It's in really solid shape and has been so dependable for me over the years. Whether you're cruising around town or headed out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
